  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 3507d679efa283143b52308c9a6a3292, type: 3}
  m_Name: Question_14
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestionData
  question: Which of the following is the level of AI that is more versatile, can
    handle a wider range of related tasks, and is focused on integrating AI within
    specific business processes?
  answers:
  - General AI
  - Broad AI
  - Narrow AI
  maxSelections: 1
  correctAnswerIndices: 01000000
  correctMessage: Broad AI is a midpoint between Narrow AI and General AI and can
    handle a wider range of related tasks than Narrow AI, while focusing on integrating
    AI within specific business processes. Broad AI is not able to perform all of
    the intellectual tasks that humans can.
  incorrectMessage: Not quite. Consider which level of AI serves as a bridge between
    more specialized AI systems and the hypothetical, more advanced level that has
    the ability to do the intellectual tasks that humans can do.
